title: inthamarmi vanuchu
sahitya:
intamarmi vanucu neruganaiti nika EmisEya dalaci nAvO nannu

anupallavi

 antarangamunanunna marmamerigi Adarimpa madilO daya rAdAyE

caraNam

 Emi sEyudunu toli janmamuna nOmu phala migula nAyegadaneru 
rAmacandrapura vara shrI vEnkaTaramaNa bhAgavata sutuDaiyuNTiyu
